            </div>
          </figure>
          <div class="card-body lg:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex gap-2 mb-2">
              <div class="badge badge-primary">Featured</div>
              <div class="badge badge-outline">React</div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="card-title text-3xl">
              Building Scalable React Applications: A Complete Guide
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/70">
              An in-depth exploration of architectural patterns, state management strategies, and
              best practices for building large-scale React applications that are maintainable and
              performant.
            </p>
